transcript:get the transcript of youtube video https://www.youtube.com/shorts/Y83wbleLeUA
word_count_for_salt: count how many times the word "salt" appear
word_count_for_sodium: count how many times the word "sodium" appear

output the following json {
  transcript: {transcript}
  word_count_for_salt: {word_count_for_salt}
  word_count_for_sodium: {word_count_for_sodium}
}
